OL,3,CDrivers 'racing' before mum and
OL,4,Cdaughter mown down, trial told
OL,6,FTwo drivers were "racing" before a
OL,7,Fmother and her four-year-old daughter
OL,8,Fwere mown down and killed as they
OL,9,Fwalked to nursery, a court has heard.
OL,11,FJustyna Hulboj, 27, and her daughter
OL,12,FLena Czepczor died when they were hit
OL,13,Fby an Audi TT which mounted the
OL,14,Fpavement on Scott Hill Road in Leeds
OL,15,Fon the morning of 16 January 2023.
OL,17,FThe car's driver, Hardeep Bhachu, 27,
OL,18,Fhas already admitted causing their
OL,19,Fdeaths by dangerous driving.
