OL,6,FBut a second man, Jasskamal Riyat, 35,
OL,7,Fof Buckstone Avenue, Leeds, denies the
OL,8,Fcharges and is on trial at Leeds Crown
OL,9,FCourt.
OL,11,FOpening the prosecution's case Carmel
OL,12,FPearson said Riyat was driving a BMW
OL,13,Fat the time of the collision.
OL,15,FShe said: "This defendant was also
OL,16,Fdriving dangerously on the same road.
