OL,3,CDrivers 'racing' before mum and
OL,4,Cdaughter mown down, trial told
OL,6,F"It is my case that together they
OL,7,Fdrove dangerously on Scott Hall Road
OL,8,Fat speed. It looked to other road
OL,9,Fusers to be rapid... braking heavily
OL,10,Fand moving in and out dangerously in
OL,11,Ffront of other road users.
OL,13,F"It is described by witnesses in a way
OL,14,Fthat it makes it clear they were
OL,15,Fracing."
OL,17,FMs Pearson said the two men did not
OL,18,Fknow each other but "came to be side-
OL,19,Fby-side at traffic lights".
