OL,6,FShe said: "When the lights changed,
OL,7,Fthe driving that led to the deaths
OL,8,Fbegan.
OL,10,F"This defendant drove at speed from
OL,11,Fthose lights ahead of Bhachu."
OL,13,FShe said dashcam footage had audio
OL,14,Fwhich revealed the BMW revved its
OL,15,Fengine.
OL,17,FThe court heard the pair had a
OL,18,Fconversation through their open
OL,19,Fwindows at a set of red traffic lights.
