OL,6,FMs Carmel said: "We have prepared a
OL,7,Ftranscript of what was said. It is my
OL,8,Fcase that what can be heard is a
OL,9,Fdiscussion about the horsepower of
OL,10,FBhachu's car, 'full throttle' and
OL,11,Fthanking the defendant for the
OL,12,Fcompliment he has just paid him. He
OL,13,Fsays 'thanks bro'."
OL,15,FThe court heard the two cars
OL,16,F"travelled in convoy" down Scott Hall
OL,17,FRoad.
