OL,3,CDrivers 'racing' before mum and
OL,4,Cdaughter mown down, trial told
OL,6,F"They undertook some vehicles and
OL,7,Fovertook others," she said. "They were
OL,8,Ftogether throughout matching each
OL,9,Fother's speed, mimicking each other's
OL,10,Fdriving."
OL,12,FShortly before the collision both cars
OL,13,Fstopped at another set of red lights.
OL,15,FMs Carmel said: "As they were at those
OL,16,Flights, this defendant got his phone
OL,17,Fout and held his phone on the steering
OL,18,Fwheel.
