OL,3,CDrivers 'racing' before mum and
OL,4,Cdaughter mown down, trial told
OL,6,F"The Audi was in front, he was behind
OL,7,Fand he could be heard to say 'watch
OL,8,Fthis guy let it off'.
OL,10,F"Bhachu set off at excessive speed.
OL,11,FThis defendant set out also at speed.
OL,12,FHe was still filming and his
OL,13,Fspeedometer shows him travelling at
OL,14,F50mph.
OL,16,F"As the mother and daughter stood on
OL,17,Fthe pavement, the Audi left the
OL,18,Fcarriageway and hit the curb, causing
OL,19,Fit to spin, mounting the curb and
OL,20,Fcolliding with the mother and
OL,21,Fdaughter, killing them."
