OL,4,Cdaughter mown down, trial told
OL,6,FThe court heard Riyat drove to work
OL,7,Fafter the incident. He later attended
OL,8,Fa medical walk-in centre for a lump in
OL,9,Fhis chest and exchanged messages with
OL,10,Fa work colleague and sent the video
OL,11,Ffrom his mobile phone.
OL,13,FMs Carmel said: "Just because this
OL,14,Fdefendant's car didn't strike those
OL,15,Fpedestrians, it doesn't mean he wasn't
OL,16,Fresponsible for those deaths.
OL,18,F"His behaviour prior to the collision
OL,19,Fis what makes him responsible for
OL,20,Ftheir deaths."
